Beef Shoulder
Beef bones
Beef Ribs


Create a bouquet garnis with the celery, parsley, cilantro, and thyme.
Bring a pot to a boil.
Add beef bones, a halved onion, 2 halved bulbs of garlic, the bouquet garnis, a few tbsp of salt, and some beef broth.
Cook over medium heat for 2 hours.
After 1 hour add 1kg of beef shoulder and ribs, and our vegetables
Serve once vegetables are ready.


